        "summary": "Get Dagster run status",
        "description": "Return the current status of a Dagster run. Queries Dagster directly \u2014 the local `run` Postgres table is not used (that requires auth context from F-008/F-018). Status values: 'running', 'success', 'failure'. Requires a valid Bearer JWT (F-008).",
        "operationId": "get_run_status_api_runs__run_id__get",
